Package: remimazolamPKPD
Type: Package
Title: Remimazolam Pharmacokinetic and Pharmacodynamic Calculator
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Yasuhiro Suzuki
Maintainer: Yasuhiro Suzuki <y.suzuki@example.com>
Description: Precise pharmacokinetic and pharmacodynamic calculations for remimazolam 
    based on the Masui 2022 population pharmacokinetic model. Implements high-precision 
    numerical integration using the 4th-order Runge-Kutta method for accurate simulation 
    of drug concentrations in plasma and effect-site compartments.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
